episodes.title: Have You Accidentally Almost Joined a Cult?
episodes.description: Ever been to a Beach Boys concert that turned out to be a cult meetup? We have. This week, we’re swapping stories of accidental cult run-ins, MLMs we reluctantly bought into, and how the PTA might just be the most socially acceptable cult out there. And because we clearly have what it takes, we’re starting our own cult—there will be free gifts, good snacks, and 90s gangsta rap!
